00:12:21.824 --> 00:12:22.909
Da! Mulțumesc!

00:12:27.538 --> 00:12:28.873
Ne dai bani de gustări?

00:12:31.960 --> 00:12:32.794
Sigur.

00:12:34.295 --> 00:12:35.129
De ce nu?

00:12:35.213 --> 00:12:36.756
- Mulțumesc!
- Bine, hai!

00:12:37.715 --> 00:12:39.300
